00:12:58.980 --> 00:13:00.580
Lütfen kaç,

00:13:00.580 --> 00:13:03.000
Date-san!

00:13:04.040 --> 00:13:06.590
Kahretsin...

00:13:32.450 --> 00:13:33.590
<i>Elveda,</i>

00:13:34.570 --> 00:13:36.320
